metadata.name: Smell Like a Skate Goblin
metadata.description:
Must. Sewage. Concrete. Metal. 

"Send us your credit card info and we'll get you smellin' like a true skate goblin after just 3 easy payments."

Ink on 11 inch by 14 inch bristol paper.
Drawn over 5 weeks. 

First appearance of Gregg Goblo
